*libbsd-0.8.0-r1 (11 Jan 2016)

  11 Jan 2016; Ian Stakenvicius <axs@gentoo.org> +libbsd-0.8.0-r1.ebuild:
  convert to multlib

  multilib is needed to support samba-4 (new rdep)

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.26

*libbsd-0.8.1-r1 (12 Jan 2016)

  12 Jan 2016; Ian Stakenvicius <axs@gentoo.org> -libbsd-0.8.0-r1.ebuild,
  +libbsd-0.8.1-r1.ebuild:
  bump multilib revision to 0.8.1

  libbsd-0.8.0 has a headers dependency on openssl, which we want to avoid
  especially on multilib.

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.26

  15 Jan 2016; Ian Stakenvicius <axs@gentoo.org> libbsd-0.8.1-r1.ebuild:
  drop errant dodoc from 0.8.1-r1, bug 571856

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.26

